Paper: hep-th/9908173

Date: 1999-08-26

Title: Loss of Causality in Discretized Light-Cone Quantisation

Authors: T. Heinzl, H. Kr\"oger and N. Scheu

Comments: Text (REVTEX file) + 4 figures (4 epsf files + 4 ps files)

We demonstrate that front form quantisation with periodicity in a compactlight-like direction (discretized light-cone quantisation) violatesmicrocausality.